    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>撕裂世界中的团结故事</strong>     </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486450/extras/9bedb1edd267f8dac163ab7e4f9de63d.poster.avif?t=1771341225\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486450/extras/9bedb1edd267f8dac163ab7e4f9de63d.webm?t=1771341225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486450/extras/9bedb1edd267f8dac163ab7e4f9de63d.mp4?t=1771341225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一场仪式，本该让守护者登神，赋予他们改变世界的异能，结果却以失败而告终。自此之后，孤寂与绝望的迷雾便席卷了埃泰尔大陆…… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幽灵苏醒时，发现自已的记忆一片空白，却不知他正是仅存的一丝希望。踏上英勇的冒险之旅，集结能够恢复世界平衡的伙伴，在这段温暖感人的故事中找回你的过往。是时候一起开启新篇章了！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486450/extras/726f595f6d249b88a65f50d8fe888160.poster.avif?t=1771341225\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486450/extras/726f595f6d249b88a65f50d8fe888160.webm?t=1771341225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486450/extras/726f595f6d249b88a65f50d8fe888160.mp4?t=1771341225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>净化心灵之路</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《孤独公会》中，人与人之间的关系就是一切。队伍强大与否取决于每位成员的实力，而你则要与新朋友建立深厚的羁绊，帮助他们在各自的冲突中找到内心的力量。六位个性迥异的伙伴组成了这支边缘人队伍，每个人都有自己的故事与挣扎。在战斗与探索中无缝切换角色，解锁支线任务与全新能力，到营火边与伙伴来一场暖心对谈。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486450/extras/bb1684d88068a932fdede201877d741e.poster.avif?t=1771341225\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486450/extras/bb1684d88068a932fdede201877d741e.webm?t=1771341225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486450/extras/bb1684d88068a932fdede201877d741e.mp4?t=1771341225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>紧张刺激的战斗流程</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幽灵会与参战的英雄“联结”，帮助他们变得更加强大。在精彩刺激的战斗中检验自己的实力，随时切换不同角色，还能用巧妙的组合技伏击敌人。打造契合你游戏风格的梦之队，尝试炫酷而独特的英雄搭配，与伙伴并肩携手，在埃泰尔闯出一片天。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486450/extras/b0e296b199df10897e8e2cdd2c0aa34f.poster.avif?t=1771341225\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486450/extras/b0e296b199df10897e8e2cdd2c0aa34f.webm?t=1771341225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486450/extras/b0e296b199df10897e8e2cdd2c0aa34f.mp4?t=1771341225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>值得守护的绚丽世界</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >埃泰尔是一个手绘风格的魔法世界，充满了魅力与秘密。在五个风格迥异的区域中，栖息着古老的文明与鲜活的传奇。与同伴协作解谜，揭开尘封已久的秘密，冲破无人能够独闯的重重险关。旅途中，你将发现无数闪亮的宝物，既有赠予朋友的礼物，也有助你前行的神器，还有能够强化小队战力的战利品。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界虽孤独，但你不必独行。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486450/extras/c5e6a453f66efe6389ee6156acf98572.poster.avif?t=1771341225\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486450/extras/c5e6a453f66efe6389ee6156acf98572.webm?t=1771341225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486450/extras/c5e6a453f66efe6389ee6156acf98572.mp4?t=1771341225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"></h2>",
